.TH man 1 "17/06/2021" "1.0" "KingsAndShips man page"
.SH NAME
.B KingsAndShips@PROJECT_VERSION@
 \- 2D isometric Tower defense game.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingsandships
.RI [ OPTIONS ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
 The king is going back with his ships, but you have taken
 his throne during his journey. You don't want him to go back.
 Organize your defense to push him back away and enjoy your new lifestyle.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -v
verbose mode

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B l
next level

.TP
.B n
send next wave

.TP
.B r
reset level

.TP
.B d
debug mode

.TP
.B dp
debug get access to the debug path mode

.TP
.B q
quit

.SH SEE ALSO
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
